{
  "id": "adv_event_2206_01_05",
  "title": "最後の\nフレーズ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――その夜、星見プロの東京寮",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――That night‚ at the Hoshimi City Tokyo dormitory of Hoshimi Productions.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "endTime": 2.2600000381,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2600
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_05-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "ただいまー！\nすっかり遅くなっちゃった……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We're home!\nWe ended up coming home so late…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.2666666667,
      "endTime": 7.4655781428,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 366.66666660000004
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 7.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_05-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "お、おかえりなさい……！\nどこか出掛けてたの？　遅かったから心配したよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-Welcome back…!\nDid you go somewhere? I was worried because it was late.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.6666666667,
      "endTime": 14.6879138629,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 14.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_05-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと息抜きをしに\n休むどころか、逆に体力、使い果たしたけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We took a little break.\nInstead of resting‚ we ended up using up more energy…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.9,
      "endTime": 22.2870065689,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 22.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_05-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんだ\n……でもちょっと、安心した",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see.\n…But I'm a little relieved.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.5,
      "endTime": 26.866666666700002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 27.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_05-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "三人とも、何か吹っ切れたような顔してるし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "All three of you have a look as if you've let something go.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.2,
      "endTime": 30.7568027973,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 31.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_05-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ！　分かっちゃう？\nそれじゃあ早速、ミーティング始めちゃおっか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe! Can you tell?\nThen‚ let's start the meeting right away.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.1,
      "endTime": 37.7350114822,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 38
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_05-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "ミーティング……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Meeting…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38,
      "endTime": 39.2795238376,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_05-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "うん！\n新曲の歌詞について、だよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah!\nIt's about the lyrics of the new song.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.4666666667,
      "endTime": 43.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_05-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "埋まらずにいた、最後のワンフレーズ……\nそれが、「この指とまれ」……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The last phrase that was missing…\nIt's \"Catch this finger!\"…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.4333333333,
      "endTime": 53.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_05-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "うん、ステキなフレーズだと思う\nサニピらしいって言うか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I think it's a wonderful phrase.\nIt's very Sunny Peace-like.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.6666666667,
      "endTime": 58.716666666600005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_05-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "でしょ？　その子が「この指とまれ」って言って\nみんながワァって集まった時……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right? That girl said‚ \"Catch this finger\"\nand when everyone gathered…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.9333333333,
      "endTime": 65.8274605116,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_05-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "沢山の笑顔がそこにあって\n一つに繋がれた気がしたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There were so many smiles there‚\nand I felt like we were all connected.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.1333333333,
      "endTime": 70.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_05-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "沢山のピースが、寄り集まって、絆になる\n「この指とまれ」は、その象徴……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Many pieces coming together‚ forming bonds.\n\"Catch this finger\" is the symbol of that…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.0333333333,
      "endTime": 79.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_05-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "何気ない言葉だけど、だからこそ\n誰の胸にも届くフレーズだって思うわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's just a simple phrase‚ but that's why…\nI think it's a phrase that can reach anyone's heart.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.7666666667,
      "endTime": 86.26666666669999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_05-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "まさしく、私達が目指してるアイドル像だよね\nだから、これでいこうって思うの……ううん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Exactly‚ it's the idol image we're aiming for.\nThat's why I wish to go with this…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.5,
      "endTime": 96.0666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_05-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "これでいきたい\nこの言葉を乗せた詞で、ファンのみんなと繋がりたい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ I want to go with this.\nI want to connect with all the fans through these lyrics.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.3,
      "endTime": 102.03333333329999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_05-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、異論なんてない\nさくら達が見つけてきた言葉を信じるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ there's no dissenting opinion.\nI believe in the words you've discovered‚ Sakura.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.2,
      "endTime": 107.7317008972,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_05-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "わ、私も……！　改めて歌詞全部読んでみたけど\n胸がいっぱいになるくらい、ステキだから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I also…! I read through the lyrics again‚\nand they're so wonderful that my heart is full…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.0666666667,
      "endTime": 117.06437670390001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_05-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "ようやく、スランプ抜け出して、完成\n……長い戦いだった……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Finally‚ I've overcome the slump and completed it.\n…It was a long battle…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.5,
      "endTime": 124.8262813569,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_05-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "雫ちゃんったら……\nこの後、歌とダンスの練習も控えてるのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ Shizuku-chan… .\nYou still have singing and dancing practice after this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.0333333333,
      "endTime": 131.2055099805,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_05-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "で、でも、とりあえずは完成したね。お疲れ様\n一時はどうなるかと思ったけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "B-But for now‚ it's completed. Good job.\nI thought it might not work out at one point‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.4,
      "endTime": 139.6167346956,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_05-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "結局、いつものさくらちゃんらしい決着だね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In the end‚ it's a typical Sakura-chan resolution.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.9666666667,
      "endTime": 144,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_05-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "……へ？　そう、かな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Huh? Is that so?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.2666666667,
      "endTime": 147.31197268169998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_05-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "さくらには、周囲を魅了する天性の何かが備わってて\nいつだって気付けば、答えを引き寄せている……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura has a natural charm that captivates those around her.\nWhenever I realize it‚ she's always attracting the answers…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.7,
      "endTime": 155.920861721,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_05-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "そういうところが、さくららしいってことよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's what makes Sakura who she is.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.2333333333,
      "endTime": 159.59410432180002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
